# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This is the main culprit: target/ contains compiled classes, the fat jar, and
# every downloaded dependency jar. Without this exclusion, oc start-build
# uploads hundreds of MB before the OpenShift build even starts.
target/

